      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DIM SIM RIXI (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (22.75) in a Grade 5 at Shepparton. Should bounce back. ROOSTER LEGS (1) ran good time (22.40) winning a Grade 5 three back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing fourth at Geelong. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. ARGYLE EMMA (2) was in the minors two back (22.49) at this track but ran below best last time at Shepparton, finishing 7th. Has a good record here at this journey. Has performed well from this box with a win and 10 minor placings to her name from 18 starts. Can do much better this time. PAW LARA (8) is a last-start placegetter with solid claims again.",
